<body>
<section class="advantages-page">

  <header class="adv-hero">
    <div class="adv-hero__inner">
      <h1 class="adv-title">Why create a Company Page on <span class="adv-brand">Jeunesse 243</span>?</h1>

      <p class="adv-subtitle">
        Give your organization a professional showcase and access an ecosystem dedicated to employment,
        training, and youth entrepreneurship.
      </p>

      <div class="adv-cta">
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" onclick="window.open(\'m/listing/browse/my&filter=add_listing\',\'_self\');">
          <i class="sys-icon sign-out"> </i><strong>Create my company page</strong>
        </button>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="m/listing/home/">Browse the directory</a>
      </div>

      <div class="adv-badges">
        <span class="badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i>Visibility</span>
        <span class="badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-tie"></i>Recruitment</span>
        <span class="badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i>Training</span>
        <span class="badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-handshake"></i>Partnerships</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="adv-content">
    <div class="adv-grid">

      <article class="adv-card">
        <h2 class="adv-card__title"><i class="fa-solid fa-bullhorn"></i>Visibility and credibility</h2>
        <p class="adv-card__text">
          Create an official page to present your activity, services, sector, location,
          and essential information. Strengthen trust among young talents and partners.
        </p>
        <ul class="adv-list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Public and accessible page</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Logo, description, sector, location</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Professional brand image</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="adv-card">
        <h2 class="adv-card__title"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-tie"></i>Simplified recruitment</h2>
        <p class="adv-card__text">
          Post job offers and receive targeted applications. Your company page becomes
          a direct entry point to attract motivated profiles.
        </p>
        <ul class="adv-list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Job posting</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Access to an active youth community</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Time-saving candidate screening</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="adv-card">
        <h2 class="adv-card__title"><i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i>Training and skills development</h2>
        <p class="adv-card__text">
          Offer training programs, showcase your expertise, and identify emerging talent.
          Position your organization as a driver of human development.
        </p>
        <ul class="adv-list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Training offers publication</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Visibility among learners</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Expertise promotion</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="adv-card">
        <h2 class="adv-card__title"><i class="fa-solid fa-diagram-project"></i>Opportunities and projects</h2>
        <p class="adv-card__text">
          Connect with other companies, project holders, and partners.
          Develop collaborations and discover opportunities in your sector.
        </p>
        <ul class="adv-list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Access to the project bank</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Partnerships and networking</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Sector visibility</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="adv-card">
        <h2 class="adv-card__title"><i class="fa-solid fa-heart-circle-check"></i>Brand image and social impact</h2>
        <p class="adv-card__text">
          Showcase your commitment to employment and training.
          Active presence strengthens your credibility and influence within the ecosystem.
        </p>
        <ul class="adv-list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Visible commitment to youth</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Trust building</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Contribution to the local economy</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="adv-card">
        <h2 class="adv-card__title"><i class="fa-solid fa-sliders"></i>Simplicity and control</h2>
        <p class="adv-card__text">
          Manage your page autonomously: updates, publications, information, and administration.
          You remain in full control of your content.
        </p>
        <ul class="adv-list">
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Quick setup</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Autonomous updates</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i>Ability to assign administrators</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

    </div>

    <section class="adv-faq">
      <h2 class="adv-section-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i>Frequently asked questions</h2>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i>Who can create a company page?</summary>
        <p>
          Any legally established company, organization, association, or structure
          wishing to present its activities and interact with the Jeunesse 243 community.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i>Is the company page public?</summary>
        <p>
          Yes. It can be viewed in the directory and shared via a link.
          Some actions (applications, messages) may require login depending on your settings.
        </p>
      </details>

      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i>What can I publish on my page?</summary>
        <p>
          You can share essential information about your company, including your products and services.
          Your page also allows you to publish <b>job offers</b>, <b>training opportunities</b>,
          <b>projects</b>, <b>events</b>, and <b>news</b>, while updating your information <b>autonomously</b>.
        </p>
      </details>
    </section>

    <section class="adv-final-cta">
      <div class="adv-final-cta__inner">
        <h2 class="adv-final-cta__title"><i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i>Ready to create your company page?</h2>
        <p class="adv-final-cta__text">
          Give visibility to your organization, publish opportunities, and connect with an active community.
        </p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" onclick="window.open(\'m/listing/browse/my&filter=add_listing\',\'_self\');">
          <i class="sys-icon sign-out"> </i><strong>Create my company page</strong>
        </button>
        <p class="adv-note">You can complete or edit your page at any time.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

</section>
</body>
</html>
