    <!-- carte DRC Executive presentation -->
    <div class="carte-executive animate-scroll">
      <h2><strong><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i> Why Jeunesse 243?</strong></h2>
<div class="apropos1ligne1"> 
  Born from the observation of <strong>high youth unemployment</strong>, the <strong>lack of access to professional information</strong>,
  and the <strong>weak connection</strong> between <strong>talents</strong> and <strong>opportunities</strong>,
  <strong>Jeunesse 243</strong> aims to become a leading digital platform for the professional integration and economic development of Congolese youth.

  <p>
   The platform enables young people to create a <b>Digital CV</b> integrated into our <b>skills directory,</b> consulted by companies, recruiters, and partners, to build their professional network, and to access job opportunities, professional training, and entrepreneurial opportunities, while facilitating connections with companies, training centers, mentors, and investors.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Jeunesse 243</strong> positions itself as a collaborative, inclusive, and results-oriented ecosystem that
    values local skills, encourages innovation, and strengthens bridges between the <strong>DRC</strong> and its
    <strong>diaspora</strong>.
  </p>
</div>

    
